snippet.title: Ali Talks Music
snippet.description:
This is not just another hip-hop and R&B channel. 

Dedicated to bringing you 'What Happened To's', album/song reviews, and discussions on various topics about your favorite hip-hop and R&B artists who have been out of the spotlight for some time. It's all here hosted by Ali! Subscribe for instant updates!
